---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="label">01</span>
      <h2>About Me</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p>
          Replace this with your actual bio. Describe who you are, what you work on,
          and what motivates your research or practice. Keep it personal and specific —
          a good bio tells a story, not just a list of credentials.
        </p>
        <p>
          You might mention where you are in your career, what problems excite you,
          and what distinguishes your approach. Two to three paragraphs is ideal.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can also include a note about collaborations, mentorship, or community
          involvement if those are important to you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-facts reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <dl>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt class="label">Affiliation</dt>
            <dd>Your University / Lab</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt class="label">Research Interests</dt>
            <dd>Topic One, Topic Two, Topic Three</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt class="label">Location</dt>
            <dd>Your City, Country</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt class="label">CV</dt>
            <dd>
              <a href="/cv.pdf" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                Download PDF ↗
              </a>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  /* Facts sidebar */
  .about-facts dl {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .fact dt {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .fact dd {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .link {
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-facts { order: -1; }
  }
</style>
